Title: Were the President of Singapore and the CEO of Temasek Holdings queuing to buy lottery tickets?
Paragraphs:
Today, 21 February 2019 – A video of 2 ladies buying lottery tickets has been circulating over WhatsApp. The video has caught attention for purportedly resembling the President of Singapore, Mdm Halimah Yacob and the Chief Executive Officer of Temasek Holdings.
Please note that this is satirical news.


Not only have we found no evidence of this being true, at least one other site has posted the videos expressing the subjects to be “lookalikes”.
So have a laugh and a good evening ahead 🙂
Author: Faizal Kamal
